- ECC skills: `nuxt4-patterns`, `e2e-testing`, `vite-patterns`.
- [Nuxt testing docs](https://nuxt.com/docs/getting-started/testing)
- [@nuxt/test-utils npm](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@nuxt/test-utils)

